
## .gitignore que SÍ funciona

```gitignore
# Entorno virtual
venv/
env/
ENV/

# Archivos sensibles
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# QR generados
test/*.png

# PyInstaller
build/
dist/
*.spec
